{"tid":33523,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"三星封鎖Note7充電功能　逼用家換機","createTime":"2016-12-10T22:43:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T23:42:54.000Z","uid":13100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"80f014efbf50c6ad53bbda539e5eed7f6f5baef1","tid":33523,"uid":13100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T22:43:59.000Z","msg":"三星自今年8月推出 Galaxy Note7以來，發生多宗爆炸事件，結果手提電話終於在10月全面停售，並展開全球回收。然而，直到今時今日，仍然有人未換機，在美國就有93%買家更換，但仍未達到100%。 有見及此，三星決定在12月中在美國發佈一個針對Note7的軟件更新，用家下載之後，將無法充電及上網，當電源耗盡之後就變相令電話報廢。 不過並非所有美國電訊商同意發佈更新，Verizon就指此舉會令用家在聖誕期間未能聯絡家人，但就會呼籲用家盡早交還電話。<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-10-2016/34455\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F12-10-2016%2F34455&d=ammElTl8ef0XgIZwl6iYv2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=bdebcd84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-10-2016/34455</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2016"},{"pid":"f32339025ec64624d1e1f4736e947cfbda405f69","tid":33523,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T22:45:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 電子垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52160871b20beb79c08a47399518ab61f0d202ec","tid":33523,"uid":59587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T22:50:30.000Z","msg":"執柒佢啦"},{"pid":"128e92864b49ad16ad58fdf65bc270f4b754f8ce","tid":33523,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T23:43:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"893f32aa10da8f62cd06f2742c46bd0288b4c2a3","tid":33523,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T00:13:16.000Z","msg":"美國佬梗係等佢爆先後告鳩你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2b173ef9fa69a34c636abafa50956621a424d7","tid":33523,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T00:21:4